    <text type="letter"> 
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="upa.00125.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <p>Dave, I send a couple copies of my pho's, one for the children each&#8212;(If I
            knew their first names I w'd have written on)</p>
            <closer>
            <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
                <p>Have just had my breakfast&#8212;hot buckwheat cakes with syrup &#38; a cup of
                tea&#8212;<hi rend="underline">Merry Christmas to you &#38; all</hi></p>
            </postscript>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
